Issue Digital Certificates from Sub CA

Generate some server’s private key:

openssl genpkey -algorithm RSA -out server.key

Generate CSR for an end entity (e.g. some server):

openssl req -new -key server.key -out server.csr

Sign the CSR Sith sub CA:

openssl x509 -req -in server.csr -CA sub.crt -CAkey sub.key
-CAcreateserial -out server.crt -days 365 -ext server.ext

View the file in a readable format:

openssl x509 -in server.crt -text -noout

